{"tid":2242004,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony 棋差一着 PS5 商標印度被搶先註冊","createTime":"2020-10-13T16:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T12:24:20.000Z","uid":252078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39c6ec6b27b5c4e2645e56c8d85b2fbd83b5ced4","tid":2242004,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"當全球不少遊戲迷期待 PS5 的推出，Sony 在其中兩個人口龐大的市場卻可能出現阻滯。早前公佈 PS5 的上市日期時，中國市場屬於待定狀態，現在全球人口第二多的印度市場，能否以 PS5 名義推出新遊戲主機亦有疑問。<br />\n<br />\n網站 The Mako Reactor 日前報導指，根據印度當局公開的資料，印度新德里一名居民 Hitesh Awani 於去年 10 月將 PS5 商標申請註冊。此舉將會導致 Sony 無法使用 PS5 作為商標，甚至影響他們將 PS5 主機在印度上市的計劃。報導指 Sony 相信已經採取對應措施，就 Awani 的商標註冊提出反對，而資料顯示現時該商標申請標注為「反對」，估計 Sony 正循著官方途徑嘗試取得 PS5 商標。"},{"pid":"a79519db2de677a7bdf5c8090aedf4aa8945687d","tid":2242004,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"今次又要攞幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc6758cbd3c1171279400d3cbb0c15939772150","tid":2242004,"uid":103799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"應該ps6 7 8 9 都比人注冊曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cb8c98e348b5190cebf2949c59f0034a9665c3","tid":2242004,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc6758cbd3c1171279400d3cbb0c15939772150","tid":2242004,"uid":103799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"應該ps6 7 8 9 都比人注冊曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"註冊黎賣印度咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88733b40ab173704995dc8f80a71f5720c33827a","tid":2242004,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc6758cbd3c1171279400d3cbb0c15939772150","tid":2242004,"uid":103799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"應該ps6 